metadata.name: Цвет #144
metadata.description:
Цвет (Eng.: Colour) is the 4th and last collection of my Suprematic series.
Colours have escaped the shapes, transcended into the infinite space.

——————

Watch in fullscreen for a better experience.
Rendering takes around 30-40 seconds at 60 fps, might take longer on older devices.
Press [Arrow Up / Down] to increase / decrease the drawing speed.
Press [1…6] to change the image resolution up to 10k.
Press [P] to pause.
Press [S] when the image is paused or rendered to save it.

Created using p5.js.
License: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

——————

hrunz. — Sep. 2022.
